{"tid":400114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍長拖都收到好人卡","createTime":"2017-09-14T13:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T10:32:54.000Z","uid":101733,"like":80,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7de21f7eefaca17ad8924df0dc3f27a7c40b5850","tid":400114,"uid":101733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:53:16.000Z","msg":"第一次拍拖拍左6-7年<br />\n比佢帽過 復合過再帽過<br />\n最後得到既<br />\n「對唔住...多謝你一路以嚟都對我好好...你係我最信任既人」<br />\n<br />\n第二次拍拖拍左3-4年<br />\n對我都好好既<br />\n當我以為可以穩定落嚟<br />\n佢一句<br />\n「對唔住...我發現對你無晒感覺...我唔想呃你繼續同你一齊...多謝你平時咁錫我對我咁好」<br />\n咁就收鳩我皮<br />\n<br />\n點解啲女人咁善變？<br />\n點解感覺話無就無？<br />\n點撚解要咁對我啊？"},{"pid":"73dcd197b1eacac2adb40cf41aca20dccd7ffeda","tid":400114,"uid":47480,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"砌部勁啲既女過世仲好"},{"pid":"0ab3153c4123144da2d02ffe18e98314794f63f6","tid":400114,"uid":101733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>砌部勁啲既女過世仲好</blockquote><br />\n同mary有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816b191eb0e262e6161337e763cb8ad5a23afec2","tid":400114,"uid":76105,"like":27,"dislike":13,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"一定係你問題 ， 拍得耐以為佢唔會走， 驚喜又無 關心又無 ，出街又掛住篤電話 返到屋企又淨係打機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2294c00334ae6df1e6c783873a7e2d75c55a5b9","tid":400114,"uid":81915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:05:40.000Z","msg":"男人都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d4e95d22fed378030e13697442d0d3a12de926","tid":400114,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0